data.title: 100 Most Popular Baby Names of 2017
data.meta_description: The most popular baby names of 2017 (so far) are here! Check out what names have made the list this year. Do you have any favorites?
data.text:
Some parents have an easy time choosing their child’s name. Some parents pour over books searching and make lists searching for the perfect designation. Whatever the case, choosing your child’s name is an important part of their identity, so, no pressure, right?

BabyCenter recently released their latest list of top 50 baby names of 2017 so far. Take a look at the list below and tell us what you think!

The Most Popular Baby Names of 2017

RANK GIRLS BOYS 1 Emma Noah 2 Olivia Liam 3 Isabella Mason 4 Ava Aiden 5 Mia Ethan 6 Sophia Oliver 7 Amelia Elijah 8 Charlotte James 9 Harper Lucas 10 Aria Jacob 11 Emily Benjamin 12 Abigail Jackson 13 Avery Logan 14 Madison Alexander 15 Ella Sebastian 16 Mila Carter 17 Sofia Gabriel 18 Scarlett Luke 19 Evelyn Matthew 20 Layla Jayden 21 Lily Michael 22 Chloe Jack 23 Aubrey William 24 Riley Jaxon 25 Penelope Wyatt 26 Grace Daniel 27 Zoey Grayson 28 Ellie Henry 29 Nora Owen 30 Elizabeth Josiah 31 Stella Levi 32 Natalie Samuel 33 Skylar David 34 Luna Joseph 35 Hannah Adam 36 Eva Hunter 37 Addison Julian 38 Aaliyah Isaiah 39 Savannah Joshua 40 Victoria Muhammad 41 Lillian Caleb 42 Violet Jordan 43 Maya John 44 Hazel Connor 45 Lucy Nathan 46 Audrey Andrew 47 Paisley Isaac 48 Leah Ryan 49 Brooklyn Anthony 50 Maria Eli

What are your favorite baby names? Do you care if your child’s name is popular? We’d love to hear!
